					</p>
					<a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mt-3">Начать без подготовки</a>
					<div class="d-flex justify-content-center mt-2 mb-3">
						<a href="#whatischatbot" data-smooth-scroll="" class="d-flex align-items-center">
							<span class="text-small ml-2">Узнать больше</span>
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-4 pb-4">
					<div class="mobile-screenshot rotate-right mx-auto layer-2" style="width: 100%;max-width: 240px;">
						<video src="/landing/video/stories.mp4" autoplay="" loop="" playsinline="" muted=""></video>
						<img src="img/iphone-xr.svg" style="width: 248px; height: 450px ;" alt="iPhone XR">
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
